KeysToEntries.story_1_2_001:
To think they can
keep up with us…
just who the hell are they…!?
KeysToEntries.story_1_2_003:
This is it?
That’s the skill
around here?
KeysToEntries.story_1_2_004:
I won’t say you’re hopeless…
but this wasn’t even worth
coming to scout…
KeysToEntries.story_1_2_005:
Well then…
maybe I’ll have a little
fun with you…!!
